@startuml
left to right direction
actor "Registered User" as User
actor Admin

rectangle "Booking System" {
  User --> (Register)
  User --> (Login)
  User --> (Logout)
  User --> (Book Session)
  User --> (View Booking)
  User --> (Edit Booking)
  User --> (Delete Booking)

  Admin --> (View Any Booking)
  Admin --> (Edit Any Booking)
  Admin --> (Delete Any Booking)
}

note right of User
- specify name, telephone, email, password to register
- login with email/password
- book one session specifying date and preferred dentist
  (dentist list with name, experience, expertise)
- view/edit/delete own booking
end note

note right of Admin
- manage any bookings
end note

@enduml